{"tid":992731,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"老細，想講咁鍾意佔我地小便宜，損失既係你","createTime":"2019-01-23T11:31:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-23T13:40:31.000Z","uid":165669,"like":4,"dislike":45,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"85ad6e30ec0d794dec2661881082b0dbeee70d4c","tid":992731,"uid":165669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T11:31:26.000Z","msg":"On9 老細成日用啲陰招佔我地便宜<br />\n<br />\n平時9屌令我地覺得自己無能<br />\n又話後生就應該比心機做野，work life balance 做掂野先學人追求<br />\n<br />\n陰招:<br />\n<br />\n1) 講到啲野好急，要我地o長t趕起佢，做到宵夜時間，飯都未食，諗住搞掂趕返屋企訓教，佢竟然迫我是但食餐飯當ot錢無數，趕住返屋企訓教都唔比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2)自己出去見客，又話有緊要野同我地講叫我地等佢，過左放工時間都要等<br />\n點知轉頭打黎同我講，準備去見第個客，唔返公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以為咁樣好醒，贏左個幾蚊，輸左個員工，值得咩？<br />\n<br />\n正評: 炒9老細<br />\n負評: 死傻9咁都仲唔炒9老細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f929b9234c3e9ddbf6d4ed9864f0e451f874da13","tid":992731,"uid":208722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T11:32:26.000Z","msg":"重問，你狗嚟架？"},{"pid":"7d95b827dce05331d9d66f92e50e7a9e0a4c054c","tid":992731,"uid":165669,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f929b9234c3e9ddbf6d4ed9864f0e451f874da13","tid":992731,"uid":208722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T11:32:26.000Z","msg":"重問，你狗嚟架？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T11:33:36.000Z","msg":"有撚問呀，咪話左炒囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f6a7f2f77dfaa856df086758a2e42a99e3048d8","tid":992731,"uid":18354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T11:34:45.000Z","msg":"唔好走，留係度<br />\n咁都仲要開post問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a633c744d0644b7ed563cef85183d710a020a6dd","tid":992731,"uid":227691,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T1